CogniDoc — A markdown convention pack for LLM-driven projects
Copyright 2026 The CogniDoc Project Contributors

This Tier 1 (Foundation) public release contains the protocol
specifications (Semantic Beacon System, Project Signal System,
Consult-Plan-Autonomy pipeline, Mission Classification System,
Project Handshake System), templates, reference examples,
documentation, and lightweight shell tooling. It is published under
the Apache License 2.0.

Higher tiers — programmatic library, validators, parsers, generators,
hosted services — are in private development with no committed timeline.
They are not part of this distribution and are not currently available
for evaluation, early access, or purchase. See docs/upgrade-path.md
for the brief honest status.

The CogniDoc name is used as a project identifier; this repository's
content is licensed permissively under Apache 2.0 and may be used,
modified, and redistributed under those terms.
